    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208570/extras/73d423ab80529f8dfbfd3df84dccbc14.poster.avif?t=1770904194\" width=600 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208570/extras/73d423ab80529f8dfbfd3df84dccbc14.webm?t=1770904194\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208570/extras/73d423ab80529f8dfbfd3df84dccbc14.mp4?t=1770904194\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >准备好了吗？你们即将化身劫匪，开启一场胆大包天的劫盗行动！这次行动可没那么简单，超自然现象的介入可能会彻底打乱你们的计划。只要一个失误，整个团队就可能被恶灵困住。如果你们成功，将有丰厚的奖金等着你们；但如果失败……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208570/extras/6af63befdb13718473a44d608ac39a6f.webp?t=1770904194\" width=600 height=43 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208570/extras/140cee1ff5a9e618d6a561e1ab7cc838.poster.avif?t=1770904194\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208570/extras/140cee1ff5a9e618d6a561e1ab7cc838.webm?t=1770904194\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208570/extras/140cee1ff5a9e618d6a561e1ab7cc838.mp4?t=1770904194\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208570/extras/c2e5e8d87ae1366c226b3102e0c37be9.webp?t=1770904194\" width=600 height=43 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208570/extras/1097280a4b6fa8242cba97e2937de663.poster.avif?t=1770904194\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208570/extras/1097280a4b6fa8242cba97e2937de663.webm?t=1770904194\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208570/extras/1097280a4b6fa8242cba97e2937de663.mp4?t=1770904194\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208570/extras/69183ddb93917f09ff2d5e5719707ecc.webp?t=1770904194\" width=600 height=43 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208570/extras/da50ad2b132214d2fd79568fd9e2f51e.poster.avif?t=1770904194\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208570/extras/da50ad2b132214d2fd79568fd9e2f51e.webm?t=1770904194\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208570/extras/da50ad2b132214d2fd79568fd9e2f51e.mp4?t=1770904194\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208570/extras/7a219dc7327c989f21808b3e6c88f708.webp?t=1770904194\" width=600 height=43 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208570/extras/2cd3c9e558c1d2d8acbfac73841d913a.poster.avif?t=1770904194\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208570/extras/2cd3c9e558c1d2d8acbfac73841d913a.webm?t=1770904194\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208570/extras/2cd3c9e558c1d2d8acbfac73841d913a.mp4?t=1770904194\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >计划。闯入。盗窃。</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >独自一人或和朋友们一起：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索 <strong>5 种环境</strong>：拍卖行、博物馆、赌场、发电厂和邮轮</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用<strong> 50+ 种</strong>抢劫道具：入侵工具、EMP、扫描仪、摄像机、传送器、电击枪等等。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >完成 <strong>12+ 个任务目标</strong>：盗取珍贵文物、销毁证据、引爆建筑、带着巨额战利品逃出生天等等。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >盗取<strong>昂贵战利品</strong>，完成合同，赢取丰厚奖励！</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >合作。生存。逃脱。</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>8 种独特的怪物</strong>，每种都有专属能力、强项和弱点。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >动态<strong>合作玩法</strong>：解谜、完成小游戏、关闭激光和安保摄像头，分享（或偷走）战利品。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>低调潜行</strong>，时刻注意周围环境：每一步失误都可能吸引怪物。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>一起生存</strong>……或者<strong>利用你的朋友</strong>，让自己活着逃出去。</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游玩。赢得奖励。再来一次。</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>3 大黑手党派系</strong>，提升你的声望，解锁 50+ 种稀有、实用且有趣的装备。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>100+ 种定制物品</strong>，打造属于你的独特风格。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>4 个难度等级</strong>，包括噩梦模式。</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >警告</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这款游戏包含闪烁的灯光，可能不适合光敏性癫痫或其他光敏性疾病患者游玩，请玩家慎重决定是否游玩。</p>",
